Scope note

The MIT license above covers the code and documentation authored in this
repository (scripts/, webui/, tools/, sanity_checks/, the markdown
documents, and the generated site in docs/).

It does NOT cover the third-party data redistributed for research
reproducibility — the manuscript transliterations (folios/,
data/translit/), folio images (folios/*.png), and cached reference texts
(data/gutenberg_cache/, data/latin_texts/) — which retain the terms and
provenance of their original sources. See CREDITS.md for full attribution
and contact information for corrections or removal requests.
